title: BONUS - How to Stop Anxious Thoughts
description:
How are you really doing? This is the one question I’m asking my people in the midst of this season. I want to get practical today. We will talk not about the spiral going around us right now, but the spiral inside us. This will give you tools to stop spiraling anxious thoughts.

Find Get Out of Your Head book: http://getoutofyourheadbook.com

ANXIOUS THOUGHTS GUIDE: JENNIEALLEN.COM
